com.bluegosling.result

Interface Result.Visitor<T,E,R>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of result value
    E - the type of result error
    R - the type returned by the visitor
    Enclosing class:
    Result<T,E>

    public static interface Result.Visitor<T,E,R>
    A visitor of results, for implementing the visitor pattern (double-dispatch) with results.
